! ====================================================================== ! SCALE ! ======================================================================
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters det2D
! --- 2D SYMBOL ---
if det2D = 1 then CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL gs_SymbolType_m=3 ! --- 1/200 if det2D = 2 then CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL gs_SymbolType_m=4 ! --- 1/100 if det2D = 4 then CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL ! --- Symbolic
if gs_SymbolType_m=1 OR gs_SymbolType_m=2 then if ABS(A-B) > EPS then unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0,0, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 A,0, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 A,B, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 0,B, unID : unID = unID + 1 endif endif
! --- 1/50 --- IF det2D = 3 THEN
PEN gs_cont_pen ! --- Minimal Space and Hotspots ---
CALL "fa_ChairSymbol" PARAMETERS ALL gs_SymbolType_m=0
ADD2 a/2, b/2 MUL2 1, bm ADD2 -A/2, -b/2+wh/SIN(Alfa)/2-wh/COS(Beta)/2 H=MIN(A/40,B/40)
! --- Background Fill and Symbol ---
FILL gs_fill_type POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0,1, A,0,1, A,B,1, 0,B,1
POLY2_B 4, 1+4,gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 2*th,0,1, A-2*th,0,1, A-2*th,B-gs_seat_height/TAN(90-Beta),1, 2*th,B-gs_seat_height/TAN(90-Beta),1
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,-wh/SIN(Alfa),1, th,-wh/SIN(Alfa),1, th,B+wh*SIN(Alfa),1, 0,B+wh*SIN(Alfa),1
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, A,-wh/SIN(Alfa),1, A-th,-wh/SIN(Alfa),1, A-th,B+wh*SIN(Alfa),1, A,B+wh*SIN(Alfa),1
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, th,B+wh/COS(Beta),1, 2*th,B+wh/COS(Beta),1, 2*th,X4-wh*COS(Beta),1, th,X4-wh*COS(Beta),1
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, A-th,B+wh/COS(Beta),1, A-2*th,B+wh/COS(Beta),1, A-2*th,X4-wh*COS(Beta),1, A-th,X4-wh*COS(Beta),1
!!LINE2 th,(B+wh*SIN(Alfa))*0.8,A-th,(B+wh*SIN(Alfa))*0.8 !!LINE2 th,(B+wh*SIN(Alfa))*0.92,A-th,(B+wh*SIN(Alfa))*0.92 !!LINE2 th,(B+wh*SIN(Alfa))*0.85,A-th,(B+wh*SIN(Alfa))*0.85 !!LINE2 th,(B+wh*SIN(Alfa))*0.73,A-th,(B+wh*SIN(Alfa))*0.73
DEL 3
endif
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iChairModelStyle CHAIRMODEL_STYLE1 = 1 CHAIRMODEL_STYLE2 = 2 CHAIRMODEL_STYLE3 = 3 CHAIRMODEL_STYLE4 = 4 CHAIRMODEL_STYLE5 = 5 CHAIRMODEL_STYLE6 = 6 CHAIRMODEL_STYLE7 = 7
! Folding Chair 02 EPS=0.001
gs_OrigoCentered = 0
dim stSymbolTypes[16] stSymbolTypes[ 1] = `Круглый` stSymbolTypes[ 2] = `Круглый со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 3] = `Прямоугольный` stSymbolTypes[ 4] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 1` stSymbolTypes[ 5] = `Трапециевидный` stSymbolTypes[ 6] = `Трапециевидный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 7] = `Криволинейный` stSymbolTypes[ 8] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 9] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[10] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[11] = `Круглый со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[12] = `Круглый со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[13] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[14] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[15] = `Детальный 1` stSymbolTypes[16] = `Детальный 2`
IF a<0.35 THEN PARAMETERS a=0.35 IF b<0.35 THEN PARAMETERS b=0.25
toth=zzyzx-gs_seat_height Alfa= ATN((zzyzx)/B)
wh = B/20 th = A/20
X4=(gs_seat_height+toth/4)/TAN(Alfa) Y4=gs_seat_height+toth/4
Beta=ATN(ABS(X4-b)/ABS(Y4))
bm=b/(b+wh/SIN(Alfa)+wh/COS(Beta))
Symbol.Script_VL:
HIDEPARAMETER ALL "A", "B", "zzyzx"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "A" range (0,) values "B" range (0,) values "ZZYZX" range (0,) values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 0, 1, 2 values{2} "iChairModelStyle" CHAIRMODEL_STYLE1, `Стиль 1`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE2, `Стиль 2`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE3, `Стиль 3`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE4, `Стиль 4`, CHAIRMODEL_STYLE5, `Стиль 5` values "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)

if gs_detlevel_2D_m <> 4 then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_SymbolType" lock "gs_SymbolType", "gs_SymbolType_m" endif
call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters all stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=19
values "gs_seat_height" range [0.1, ZZYZX-0.1]
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif

if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow" endif
!!! ******************************** Minimal Space
values "MSFront" range [0,) VALUES "MSSide" range [0,) VALUES "MSRear" range [0,)
